What you need to know:  Victims of land grabbing in Mavoko say a governor, the governor’s brother, two lawmakers and a senior police officer are to blame for their woes. Hired men assaulted their latest victim who had gone to reclaim his property 10 days ago following a Daily Nation expose.Officials of Kamulu Housing, a company with offices in Tala, Machakos County, will record a statement at the DCI today relating to the long-running dispute.